You never know what you'll find in
an unknown place. Be very careful.

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, those people are Drivers. Their
strength is guaranteed, so they'll
manage no matter what happens.

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0004
rows.name:
So you just focus on your own
role, Rex, and don't worry.
